text.p: This module is the items,spells and equipment for SW5e.
This module does not contain a Reference Manual. This module is primarily meant to be used to populate the ITEMS and SPELLS selection button.
To see a categorized list of Armor and Weapons, use the buttons at the top of the ITEMS windows after pressing the ITEMS button.
To help with SPELL selection, use the Source and Level selectors at the bottom of the SPELL button window.
Use the above link to obtain all the most current SW5e reference PDF files.

p.b: If you find any errors or have suggestions on improvement please enter a ticket at the github site for this project.
